sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller
    participant TrustyAIService as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Pod<br/>HTTP

    Note over User,ModelMesh: Flow 1: TrustyAIService Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch notification
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PVC<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Services (80, 443)<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment (TrustyAI + OAuth)<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update TrustyAIService status<br/>Condition: Available=True

    Note over User,ModelMesh: Flow 2: User Access to TrustyAI Service

    User->>Router: HTTPS GET /apis/v1beta1/endpoint<br/>443/TCP TLS1.2+
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (service-ca cert)
    OAuthProxy->>OAuth: Validate token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    OAuth-->>OAuthProxy: Token valid + Subject Access Review
    OAuthProxy->>TrustyAIService: Proxy request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    TrustyAIService-->>OAuthProxy: JSON Response
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,ModelMesh: Flow 3: ModelMesh Integration

    Controller->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService list
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Get ModelMesh Deployments<br/>label: modelmesh-service=modelmesh-serving
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Deployment details
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment env vars<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS={trustyai-url}
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Deployment patched

    ModelMesh->>TrustyAIService: Forward inference payloads<br/>80/TCP HTTP (ClusterIP)
    TrustyAIService-->>ModelMesh: Acknowledgement

    Note over User,ModelMesh: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    User->>K8sAPI: Prometheus scrapes ServiceMonitor
    K8sAPI->>TrustyAIService: HTTP GET /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    TrustyAIService-->>K8sAPI: Prometheus metrics
    K8sAPI-->>User: Metrics data
